{"tid":2218612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"默克爾為德國電信進入中國市場出力","createTime":"2020-09-26T10:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T10:59:26.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d897d050589d28c4dfef16e032405d278d5aff43","tid":2218612,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"據德國《經濟周刊》報道，柏林將幫助德國電信（Deutsche Telekom）獲得進入中國移動通信市場的渠道。這可能是德中有關華為的交易的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n《經濟周刊》引述歐盟圈內人士消息說，默克爾親自介入，在中國接洽方面前為德國電信出力。<br />\n<br />\n布魯塞爾擔心，默克爾親自出場，可能是一個交易的一部分。在這個交易中，德國將為受到爭議的中國電信巨頭華為保持德國5G市場的開放。中方曾提供了八點反間諜協議，以緩解德國的安全憂慮。布魯塞爾對默克爾的舉動持批評態度。<br />\n<br />\n《經濟周刊》繼續報道說，德國電信否認對中國市場感興趣，因為它&ldquo;明確關注歐洲和美國&rdquo;。但是，德國電信在雲業務上與華為緊密合作，並在中國提供共享雲。估計德國政府最近將決定德國未來與華為的合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20200925-%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE%E7%82%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E4%BF%A1%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%87%BA%E5%8A%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%2F20200925-%25E9%25BB%2598%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%2588%25BE%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258A%259B&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=7b3c3602\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20200925-%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE%E7%82%BA%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E4%BF%A1%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%87%BA%E5%8A%9B</a>"},{"pid":"28a3062a594447cb180d17c23bd866f9483c8fbd","tid":2218612,"uid":134323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"肥婆又賺人仔"},{"pid":"d64e4adae797cf21010c3097ccca5410a25c5564","tid":2218612,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}